data.description: Welcome to this semi-detached home in Enola. The property features 3 bedrooms, 1 bathroom, an eat-in kitchen with a pantry, some replacement windows, central air, a private backyard, a formal living room, full basement, and the attic could be finished for a 4th bedroom or play room. The home was remodeled in 2010. Call today for more information or for your private showing.
